explore in college.

27:48.525 --> 27:50.661
- For instance? - I don't know.
You know how much

27:50.694 --> 27:53.429
I love kids, and I'd love to be
a teacher like Mr. Shue, or...

27:53.470 --> 27:54.733
or premed or something.

27:54.766 --> 27:57.069
