28:06.789 --> 28:09.450
And it's no secret what my
favorite Milton Bradley game is.

28:09.491 --> 28:11.922
Here goes his funny bone.

28:11.955 --> 28:14.090
(buzz) (quietly): Dang.

28:14.123 --> 28:17.329
