there's all these beautiful people

28:42.091 --> 28:44.051
who seem to have just come
from some secret meeting

28:44.061 --> 28:46.325
where they teach you how
to make it in the big city.

28:46.358 --> 28:49.027
What if I don't get in?
<i>You</i> didn't.

28:49.060 --> 28:51.830
You will. And if you
don't, it won't matter.

28:51.871 --> 28:54.706
You're a performer; you're
gonna find the spotlight.

28:54.739 --> 28:56.677
And you can't shy away
from your greatness

28:56.710 --> 28:58.581
just because you're afraid
you're not great enough.

28:58.614 --> 29:00.887
You have a gift,
and it wouldn't be right

29:00.920 --> 29:02.825
to let you hide that away.

29:02.858 --> 29:05.196
Thanks for knowing me.

29:05.229 --> 29:06.935
I love you.

29:06.968 --> 29:09.272
I love you, too.

29:10.737 --> 29:13.345
And we're in this together.

29:13.378 --> 29:15.612
I can't stop you
from failing, but...

29:15.645 --> 29:19.055
I can promise to make it
safe if you do.

29:19.088 --> 29:21.024
And I think Santana
should do your makeup.

29:27.034 --> 29:28.402
