29:35.105 --> 29:37.608
This is one of our
independent living classes.

29:37.641 --> 29:39.943
Students are working
on bill paying

29:39.976 --> 29:42.573
and budgeting their money.

29:42.606 --> 29:44.709
Everybody, this
is Becky Jackson.

29:44.742 --> 29:46.107
She's thinking of coming here.

29:46.148 --> 29:48.745
BOY:
Don't. This place sucks.

29:48.778 --> 29:51.482
