29:56.858 --> 29:59.930
Artie? Hell, no.
He's got herpes.

29:59.963 --> 30:00.802
Ew.

30:00.835 --> 30:02.067
Just for the record,

30:02.100 --> 30:03.902
I don't have herpes.

30:03.943 --> 30:05.745
Becky, I think

30:05.778 --> 30:07.849
