Becky, would you like

30:14.179 --> 30:16.980
to stay and watch the class for a while?
BOY: Yeah.

30:17.021 --> 30:20.418
You can sit next to me.

30:22.019 --> 30:23.091
Okay.

30:23.124 --> 30:24.956
Whatever.

30:39.180 --> 30:40.683
So, how is your name
pronounced again?

30:40.716 --> 30:41.979
Because I heard
it was "Bee-shay,"

30:42.020 --> 30:43.755
but now that
I see it spelled out,

30:43.788 --> 30:45.355
