30:51.157 --> 30:52.893
I'm... I tend to talk too much.

30:52.934 --> 30:55.100
I'm used to dealing with boys
far prettier

30:55.133 --> 30:56.963
and considerably stupider
than you.

30:56.996 --> 30:58.803
Oh, cool. Look, I
agreed to meet with you

30:58.836 --> 31:00.235
