Brownfield's eye.

31:00.268 --> 31:03.911
And I must admit,
I do respond to your look.

31:03.944 --> 31:07.680
Your Midwestern eyes
have the vacant stare

31:07.713 --> 31:08.953
of a cow's.

31:08.986 --> 31:11.128
I don't have any of those
on my roster.

31:11.156 --> 31:12.821
And you have a unique mouth.

31:12.861 --> 31:14.156
It's, like, your lips,

31:14.189 --> 31:17.088
they're kind of like...

31:17.121 --> 31:18.159
Trouty.

31:18.192 --> 31:19.526
Yes! That's it.

31:19.559 --> 31:20.861
Trouty mouth.

31:20.894 --> 31:22.664
Can I have, uh, one of these...

31:22.697 --> 31:23.832
No.

31:23.865 --> 31:25.464
So, this is how this works.

31:25.497 --> 31:26.697
These pictures...

31:26.738 --> 31:28.370
