what you think it is.

32:01.607 --> 32:03.078
You are one of

32:03.111 --> 32:05.310
10,000 beautiful boys
here in New York City,

32:05.343 --> 32:07.214
and the word that you will hear

32:07.247 --> 32:09.551
more than any other
during your brief

32:09.584 --> 32:10.921
