32:52.667 --> 32:54.266
We don't have room for this.

32:54.307 --> 32:55.874
Uh, yes, we do. Right there.

32:55.907 --> 32:58.074
Okay, seriously,
I'm not gonna be able to survive

32:58.107 --> 32:59.808
