33:29.478 --> 33:31.014
Yes. SANTANA: Oh, no.

33:31.047 --> 33:32.614
No, no, no, no, no.

33:32.647 --> 33:34.413
Do you see this?
This is what's going

33:34.446 --> 33:36.443
