I suppose that includes

39:13.200 --> 39:16.333
your hopelessly
misguided teen hobgoblins.

39:16.366 --> 39:19.034
Now, don't forget to remind them
about the myriad

39:19.067 --> 39:22.373
of show business legends born
and bred right here in Lima.

39:22.406 --> 39:24.110
And that would be
a total of one,

39:24.143 --> 39:26.037
Ms. Phyllis Diller.

39:26.078 --> 39:29.075
You know, in a few decades,
when the New Directions are all

39:29.108 --> 39:31.275
