time and remember you fondly.

39:39.517 --> 39:40.853
TINA: That's not
true, Sue Sylvester!

39:40.886 --> 39:42.357
One day, we're gonna be
big, big stars.

39:42.390 --> 39:45.029
SUE: Well, of course
you are, my dear.

39:45.062 --> 39:46.029
