I cannot imagine what goes on

40:19.013 --> 40:21.983
in your lumpish,
sexually ambiguous heads.

40:22.016 --> 40:23.384
'Cause they're nuts.

40:23.417 --> 40:24.522
Every one of them

40:24.555 --> 40:25.692
